OL,3,CPolice boss calls for creation of mega
OL,4,Cforces in England
OL,6,FInstead of the current 43 county
OL,7,Fforces, there could be 12-15 larger-
OL,8,Fsized forces in England, Sir Mark
OL,9,Fwrote in The Sunday Times.
OL,11,FHe said: "The 43-force model was
OL,12,Fdesigned in the 1960s and hasn't been
OL,13,Ffit for purpose for at least two
OL,14,Fdecades. It hinders the effective
OL,15,Fconfrontation of today's threats and
OL,16,Fstops us fully reaping the benefits of
OL,17,Ftechnology.
