OL,3,CPolice boss calls for creation of mega
OL,4,Cforces in England
OL,6,F"We need to reduce the number of
OL,7,Fforces by two-thirds, with the new
OL,8,Fbigger and fully capable regional
OL,9,Fforces supported by the best of modern
OL,10,Ftechnology and making better use of
OL,11,Fthe limited funding available."
OL,13,FHe said Chancellor Rachel Reeves'
OL,14,Fdecision to increase police funding by
OL,15,F2.3% above inflation each year in the
OL,16,Frecent spending review was
OL,17,F"disappointing".
