OL,3,CPolice boss calls for creation of mega
OL,4,Cforces in England
OL,6,FGavin Stephens, chairman of the
OL,7,FNational Police Chiefs' Council, last
OL,8,Fmonth warned forces were facing
OL,9,F"difficult choices" and some would
OL,10,F"struggle to make the numbers add up"
OL,11,Fas the cost of borrowing spirals.
OL,13,FSome have increasingly relied on
OL,14,Fborrowing, and the cost of debt is
OL,15,Fexpected to rise by 49% in the next
OL,16,Fthree years.
OL,18,F"Forces' borrowing costs have been
OL,19,Fgoing up because for the last decade,
OL,20,Flocal forces have had no capital
OL,21,Finvestment at all," he said.
