OL,3,CPolice boss calls for creation of mega
OL,4,Cforces in England
OL,6,FMr Stephens said policing needs a
OL,7,Fvariety of workers other than
OL,8,Fofficers, including cyber specialists,
OL,9,Fcrime scene investigators and digital
OL,10,Fforensic experts, in the same way that
OL,11,F"the health service is much more than
OL,12,Fjust about doctors".
OL,14,FHe added: "We know that the Government
OL,15,Fhad some very difficult choices to
OL,16,Fmake, as a consequence of this,
OL,17,Fpolicing is going to have some very
OL,18,Fdifficult choices to make too."
